					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Hindu spring festival of colours</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
</p>
<style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r1033289096">.mw-parser-output .hatnote{font-style:italic}.mw-parser-output div.hatnote{padding-left:1.6em;margin-bottom:0.5em}.mw-parser-output .hatnote i{font-style:normal}.mw-parser-output .hatnote+link+.hatnote{margin-top:-0.5em}</style><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable"><span>"Holli" redirects here. For the ice hockey player, see <a href="/wiki/Antti_H%C3%B6lli" title="Antti Hölli">Antti Hölli</a>.</span> <span>For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Holi_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Holi (disambiguation)">Holi (disambiguation)</a>.</span></div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt"> 

</p>
