<li id="cite_note-151"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-151">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1 cs1-prop-foreign-lang-source"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.6yka.com/novost/126379/oboji-svoje-ljeto-uz-bih-color-festival-28.-i-29.-jula-u-brckom">"Oboji svoje ljeto uz BiH Color Festival 28. i 29. jula u Brčkom"</a> (in Bosnian). 6yka.com. 13 July 2017.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Oboji+svoje+ljeto+uz+BiH+Color+Festival+28.+i+29.+jula+u+Br%C4%8Dkom&amp;rft.pub=6yka.com&amp;rft.date=2017-07-13&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.6yka.com%2Fnovost%2F126379%2Foboji-svoje-ljeto-uz-bih-color-festival-28.-i-29.-jula-u-brckom&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHoli" class="Z3988"></span></span>
