<li id="cite_note-152"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-152">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1 cs1-prop-foreign-lang-source"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180418161233/http://radiobrcko.ba/bih-color-festival-po-drugi-put-u-brckom/">"BiH Color Festival po drugi put u Brčkom"</a> (in Bosnian). otisak.ba. 25 July 2017. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://radiobrcko.ba/bih-color-festival-po-drugi-put-u-brckom/">the original</a> on 18 April 2018<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">17 April</span> 2018</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=BiH+Color+Festival+po+drugi+put+u+Br%C4%8Dkom&amp;rft.pub=otisak.ba&amp;rft.date=2017-07-25&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fradiobrcko.ba%2Fbih-color-festival-po-drugi-put-u-brckom%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHoli" class="Z3988"></span></span>
